Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain physiology of infatuation is\Nthe left brain, the physical. Whereas
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,with love, it's the right brain, the\Netheric.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The emotional process of infatuation is\Nfrustration, frantic, fearful,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,tormented.\NWhereas with love there's gratitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,peaceful, self-fulfilling.\NStability in infatuation is desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas with love it's enhanced.\NBody functions in infatuation are
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,impaired. Loss of appetite, loss of\Nsleep. Whereas with love, it's improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The description of infatuation is\Ncraving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas with love, it's contentment.\NPathology and infatuation is suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,despair,\Nstalking,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love there's well-being.\NJudgment in infatuation
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is impaired\Nwhereas with love it's improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Perception in infatuation is exaggerated\Nwhereas in love it's illuminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention of infatuation\Nis to possess, to own, to control, to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,capture. Whereas with love it's to be\Nwith
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,productivity and infatuation is\Ndisrupted whereas with love it's
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,enhanced.\NThe self-image in infatuation is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,inflated whereas with love it's\Npositive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Balance in infatuation is erratic\Nwhereas with love it's steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The hormone in endocrine in infatuation\Nis adrenaline and the sex hormones
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love they are endorphins\Nand oxytocin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The social image in infatuation is\Ninflated whereas with love it's
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,enhanced. The intellectual function in\Ninfatuation is to romanticize and lower
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,mind. Whereas with love it's realistic\Nand higher mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of consciousness in\Ninfatuation lowers whereas with love it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,raises.\NThe style of infatuation
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is involvement\Nhorizontal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:20:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas with love, it's alignment and\Nvertical.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Did you want to say something about\Nthis? The in uh the horizontal and the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,vertical\Nthat when you're in love, it's vertical.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying together. when there is um\Nin uh when there's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's involvement you're horizontal.\N>> Yeah. Because that's the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,between an attachment and attachment is\Nsomething different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Okay.\N>> You know, you're attached to somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean you're aligned to\Nthem. You might even kill them. You
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,know,\NI was so attached to her that I had to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,kill her when I saw her flirting with\Nsomebody else. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So alignment means that your purpose\Nyour purposes are aligned. So
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> that's why uh a spiritual\Nu
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:21:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,overall field in a relationship\Nin ensures its longevity and and the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,positive effect it has on others so that\Nyou become an example. The more you love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the more you can love.\NSometimes love is con misconceived as an
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,attachment. Attachment is one thing and\Nlove is another.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can love something and neither be\Nattached or not be attached. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N>> Relatedness and infatuation is demanding
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love it's harmonious.\NThe goal of infatuation is to satisfy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and to own. Whereas with love it's to\Nfulfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The pattern of infatuation is\Nindividualism.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:22:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas with love it's concordance.\NLoss is experienced in infatuation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with depression,\Nrage, hate and blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas loss is experienced in love with\Ngrief and regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego dynamics of love. The capacity\Nfor love increases as positionalities
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,are surrendered.\NLove is a quality of divinity and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,emerges in accord with spiritual\Npractices.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For example,\Nbe kind to everything and everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,including oneself at all times with no\Nexception.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Wow.\NLove illuminates the essence and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:23:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore the lovability of others.\N>> Do you want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes. Because this opens the heart\Ninstead of perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The the heart knows.\NSo the mind thinks and argues and and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.96,0:23:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,carries on like that. But the heart just\Ncontinues.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So even when you're very very bad. I\Nlove you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So, so you're saying that the the brain\Nwill or the thoughts would tell you one
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,thing, but the heart would tell you\Nsomething else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,>> That's true.\N>> Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So, the the mind the mind could be\Ncritical and disagree, but the heart is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.12,0:23:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,loving uh no matter what.\N>> Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So, the the heart does not put any\Nconditions on what's out there. uh only
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.91,0:23:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind does\Nthe heart I love you no matter whether
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.40,0:24:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,there's coffee in the morning or not\Nconditions
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.28,0:24:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,>> right okay\N>> love makes no demands
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> transcending level 500\Na key to making love unconditional is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.44,0:24:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to forgive.\NWith forgiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.88,0:24:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,events and people are recontextualized\Nas simply quote limited, not bad or
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.24,0:24:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,unlovable.\NForgiveness ensues from the willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.44,0:24:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of humility to surrender the world and\Nits events to divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.24,0:24:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray to the Holy Spirit for a miracle to\Nsee the truth about the situation or the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.67,0:24:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,person\Nand surrender all perceptual
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.91,0:25:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,positionalities and their egoistic gain\Nto the revelation of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.84,0:25:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, when you when you say pray to the\Nholy spirit for a miracle to see the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.20,0:25:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,truth about a situation or a person,\Nare we to forgive that person if there
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.40,0:25:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,was a conflict um or or just accept them\Nfor it is
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.24,0:25:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> because you're still seeing them the\Nsame way or you wouldn't be forgiving
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.00,0:25:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,them\Nuh
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.44,0:25:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,through the course of miracles es the\Nmiraculous occurs
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.84,0:25:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but not as a consequence of how you're\Nseeing it because you may still see it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.20,0:25:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the same way and yet it it happens. So\Nwhen I ask for a miracle, I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.48,0:26:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendering my perception of how I see\Nit and then it's transformed. And when
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.60,0:26:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's transformed,\NI see that it still is lovable. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.48,0:26:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I see that somebody I'm angry at\Ncannot help but be that way. So now
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.03,0:26:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of hating them or being angry, I\Nfeel sorry for them and I say it's too
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.64,0:26:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,bad that they can't see it the way I'm\Nseeing it. You see, cuz I know their
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.20,0:26:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,life is painful the way they are seeing\Nthe world. And when they see it my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.15,0:26:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the law the the world stops being\Npainful. Yes. Uhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.64,0:26:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Okay.\NRemember
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.64,0:26:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,this domain is one of maximum spiritual\Nopportunity with a multitude of options
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.12,0:26:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,which aid the evolution of\Nconsciousness. Therefore, one can be
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.67,0:26:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,grateful instead of resentful about the\Npast.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.88,0:27:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha said, "Rare is it to be born\Na human being. Rarer still to have heard
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.27,0:27:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of enlightenment and even rarer still to\Npursue it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.08,0:27:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love. Words that describe\Nthis energy field. Only point4% of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.27,0:27:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,people miraculous inclusive inner joy\Ncondalini energy non selective healing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.00,0:27:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,vision merciful faith essence\Ntransformative
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.88,0:27:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,ecstasy beauty selfless kindness\Nsynchronicity
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.76,0:27:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,radiant sides Perfection,\Neffortless patience, surrender,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.24,0:27:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,unlimited\Npersistence,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.36,0:28:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,emerging self with a capital S, diffuse,\Ncompassion, devotional,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.00,0:28:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,openness, saintly, rapture,\Nway of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.44,0:28:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Wowy.\Nunconditional love, joy and ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.08,0:28:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As love becomes unconditional, it begins\Nto be experienced as inner joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.24,0:28:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy arises from within each moment of\Nexistence, not from any outer source.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.88,0:28:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The hallmark of this state is\Ncompassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.55,0:28:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,At this level, people have a notable\Neffect on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.72,0:28:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Um, David, when you say that um, you\Nexperience joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.00,0:29:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> what type of joy or when you say joy,\Nwhat do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.76,0:29:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Joy is to me not just an emotional uh\Nthing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.27,0:29:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Uh, joy may occur as an emotion along\Nwith it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.48,0:29:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But joy is like\Nyou thought
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.44,0:29:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the dog was run over and killed and when\Nyou get there you realize that it was
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.12,0:29:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,only hurt a little bit and it's still\Nliving and its tail wags
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.72,0:29:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and and your heart just jumps with joy.\NThe doggy's okay, not really badly hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.44,0:29:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And so\Nyou jump with joy. Jump with joy. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.64,0:29:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I jump with joy when I get up every\Nmorning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.79,0:29:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still alive.\NMy age, you're glad to see yourself in
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.44,0:30:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the mirror every day. Hi Dave, how are\Nyou today? Oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.79,0:30:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So joy is arises within each moment\Nof existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.52,0:30:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I can't hear you.\N>> It says joy arises from within. Each
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.08,0:30:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,moment\N>> yes it's from within. It's not dependent
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.08,0:30:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,on anything out there. Whether the\Naudience laughs or not is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.96,0:30:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether they're enjoying what I'm saying\Nis irrelevant. That's their problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.27,0:30:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to be self-sufficient because the\Nradiance of divinity uh the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.12,0:30:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of love is everywhere present.\NIt's like the sun just shining
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.27,0:30:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,everywhere on the desert no matter where\Nyou go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.72,0:30:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Uhhuh.\N>> Everything happens effortlessly by
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.12,0:31:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,synchronicity.\NOne sees the world and everything in it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.39,0:31:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to be an expression of love and\Ndivinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.84,0:31:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This state is impersonal, not personal.\NIt represents the power of the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.24,0:31:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,field, not of the individual.\N>> Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.79,0:31:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> There is the capacity to love many\Npeople simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.00,0:31:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Love has no limits. Yes.\NThe more people you love, the more you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.91,0:31:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,can love.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.64,0:31:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love is the goal of the\Nmajority of spiritually committed
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.67,0:31:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,people.\NUnconditional love at 540 is a practical
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.91,0:31:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and reachable goal.\NThe goal of unconditional love is
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.36,0:32:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,reachable by very simple means. For\Nexample, quote, to live with care and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.84,0:32:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,kindness on a daily basis without\Nexception.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.24,0:32:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, a lot of us would like to\Ngive that example of living with care
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.20,0:32:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and kindness on a daily basis, but when\Nwe try to apply it, it just doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.84,0:32:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,work.\N>> So, can you give us some tips as to how
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.00,0:32:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,we could achieve that?\N>> Well, it's because of how we are viewing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.67,0:32:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the world. In other words, when we place\Nexpectations on the world, then we set
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.27,0:32:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,oursself up for disruption.\NYou know, I have no expectation that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.44,0:32:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be coffee in the kitchen in\Nthe morning or not. I have great hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.39,0:33:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It may or may not be there. You think I\Nhave great hopes that when we get home
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.36,0:33:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,today, the doggy will not have had an\Naccident in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.60,0:33:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But if doggy had an accident, I'm\Nprepared to forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.12,0:33:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So unconditionally loving means\Nno conditions. No conditions because
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.91,0:33:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the way that I am and not the way\Nthe world has to be. The doggy doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.44,0:33:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,have to be the way I want her to be. I\Nwould prefer it, but she's only a doggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.39,0:33:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And if she's got to go waw wa, she's\Ngoing to go waw wa. Hopefully not before
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.12,0:33:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we get home.\NAll right. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.96,0:33:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Okay.\N>> There is a silent
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.60,0:33:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,nonverbal\Nbenefit of being in the actual presence
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.84,0:34:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of such a teacher.\NThe silent transmission of the high
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.72,0:34:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,frequency energy of the teacher's aura\Nis referred to as the silent teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.56,0:34:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The transmission of null mind, the grace\Nof the teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.11,0:34:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the benediction\Nof the teacher. It happens of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.96,0:34:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and is not personal.\NThat's the transmission of grace by
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.83,0:34:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,virtue of the energy field of the\Nteacher which radiates forth
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.52,0:34:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,unconditionally.\NThe grace of the guru. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.59,0:34:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when we did the calibration on\Nthis to see if that was true, it, you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.76,0:34:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,know, we both kind of said, "Oh, that's\Nthat everyone had to be in the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.48,0:35:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of a teacher." Doesn't mean to be in\Nyour any teacher's presence, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.48,0:35:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Well, the Buddha transmitted it,\N>> right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.11,0:35:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah. And so, he's giving him a flower\Nis symbolic of the transmission of the
